In total, their cash registers made almost 100 million transactions on Black Friday.
The company's representative, Dan Fogelman, declared in an interview on the left-wing website Huffington Post, that they left their job - fewer than five - employees of Walmart and that the protest had been nothing more than - another trick of public relations - organized by the workers' union.
